title: [Dunstan's Farm Depot]
description: Glimpses of the starry sky are visible through high windows.  Hanging from the rafters are a number of drying animal hides.  The strong earthy scents of the straw-covered dirt floor, stacked bales of hay, and damp wood permeate the air.  Wrought-iron hooks have been affixed to the barn walls, displaying the various merchandise for sale.
